for Led Zeppelin,

01:34.294 --> 01:36.797
and his name
is John Bonham, baby.

01:36.830 --> 01:38.298
(LAUGHING) Oh, yeah.

01:42.769 --> 01:43.804
Nah, nah, nah.

01:43.837 --> 01:45.071
Here we go,
here we go.

01:45.105 --> 01:46.239
(IMITATING BILL MURRAY)
Hey, Lisa!

01:46.272 --> 01:48.241
Here's those noogies
you ordered.

01:48.274 --> 01:50.210
