of that one!

01:54.247 --> 01:56.983
It's in the hole!
It's in the hole!

01:57.017 --> 01:58.451
ALAN: Sam Weir.

02:00.220 --> 02:02.488
You really like
Bill Murray, don't you?

02:03.089 --> 02:04.758
SAM: Yeah. He's great.

02:04.791 --> 02:06.893
Bill Murray sucks, man.

02:06.927 --> 02:08.128
