02:14.134 --> 02:16.169
It's fightin' time, weird.

02:16.202 --> 02:17.403
Leave me alone, Alan.

02:17.437 --> 02:20.073
I'm sorry.
I don't speak geek.

02:20.106 --> 02:23.009
I always wanted to know
what it'd be like
to fight a girl.

02:23.043 --> 02:24.611
