you should be learning
how to socialize.

05:14.447 --> 05:16.817
That's what high school
dances are all about.

05:16.850 --> 05:18.484
No, they're not.
They're just a chance

05:18.519 --> 05:20.821
for the popular kids
to experiment with sex
in their cars.

05:20.854 --> 05:21.955
Lindsay!
Hey!

05:21.988 --> 05:23.590
LINDSAY: If that's what
you want me to do,

05:23.624 --> 05:26.359
then I'd be
happy to go.

05:26.392 --> 05:29.863
You know, there was
a girl in our school...

05:31.031 --> 05:33.233
