Lindsay...

05:58.058 --> 05:59.359
Dad.
Honey.

05:59.392 --> 06:01.728
Great. That works out perfect.

06:01.762 --> 06:03.730
I'm having
a midnight madness

06:03.764 --> 06:05.331
