Congratulations.

06:40.466 --> 06:42.035
(ALL LAUGH)

06:46.439 --> 06:47.508
Hey, Mr. K.

06:47.541 --> 06:48.842
Mr. Schweeber.

06:48.875 --> 06:49.876
