Ah, Mr. Bones, Mr. Spock.

06:59.419 --> 07:02.589
May I join you here in
the Enterprise Mess Hall?

07:02.623 --> 07:04.791
(SIGHS) I'm so hungry

07:04.825 --> 07:07.728
