(SAM LAUGHS)

07:07.761 --> 07:10.063
I... I don't get it.
Who's that?

07:10.831 --> 07:11.998
John Wayne.

07:12.432 --> 07:14.768
Oh. Okay. Yeah.

07:14.801 --> 07:17.337
Why does my mom
always put a note
in my lunch?

07:17.370 --> 07:19.472
