07:19.506 --> 07:21.975
At least your mom doesn't
write the note on the bag.

07:24.811 --> 07:26.146
(LAUGHS)

07:26.179 --> 07:27.280
Are you guys going to

07:27.313 --> 07:29.482
the Homecoming Dance?
No.

07:29.516 --> 07:31.885
I really don't
see that happening.

07:31.918 --> 07:33.286
(THUDS LOUDLY)

07:33.319 --> 07:35.689
Oh, I'm sorry. Did I crush
your twinkies?

07:35.722 --> 07:37.223
What did you
do that for?

07:37.257 --> 07:40.193
Oh, what are you gonna do,
go crying to your sister,

07:40.226 --> 07:41.828
Sam Rear?

07:41.862 --> 07:43.363
No. No, I'm not.

07:43.396 --> 07:46.733
Mr. Kowchevski.
Alan smashed my twinkies.

07:46.767 --> 07:49.235
Oh, my God.
You're such a woman.

07:51.071 --> 07:52.806
