anything better to do

07:52.839 --> 07:54.675
than to crush
Mr. Weir's dessert?

07:54.708 --> 07:57.177
Oh, well, I was just
bending down to talk to him,

07:57.210 --> 07:58.745
and I accidentally
leaned on it.

07:58.779 --> 07:59.713
I'm sorry.

07:59.746 --> 08:01.014
Why don't you
do the nice thing

08:01.047 --> 08:02.282
and buy him new ones?

08:02.315 --> 08:03.917
Oh, yes, sir.

08:05.185 --> 08:07.487
Thank you,
Mr. Kowchevski.

08:07.521 --> 08:09.790
Sam, you want
some advice?

08:09.823 --> 08:10.991
Be a man.

08:13.894 --> 08:16.262
You shouldn't let Alan
do that to you.

08:16.296 --> 08:18.164
I don't see you
doing anything!

08:19.065 --> 08:20.867
My dad tells me
to stay out of fights

08:20.901 --> 08:22.435
that don't affect me
directly.

08:22.468 --> 08:25.471
