you guys backed me up
once in a while.

08:25.506 --> 08:27.373
My sister does,
and she's a girl.

08:27.407 --> 08:28.775
Yeah, but if we
back you up,

08:28.809 --> 08:30.944
than Alan's gonna
terrorize us, too.

08:32.378 --> 08:34.114
Listen, you guys
have gotta help me,

08:34.147 --> 08:35.982
