09:18.959 --> 09:21.327
Your butt
was calling to me.

09:23.063 --> 09:24.765
Hey, Nicholas,
you get those M‐80's?

09:24.798 --> 09:26.867
NICHOLAS: I don't know.
You got the money?

09:32.205 --> 09:34.107
You guys know Lindsay?

09:34.541 --> 09:35.809
