10:00.667 --> 10:01.802
That's funny.

10:01.835 --> 10:03.069
It's a joke, right?

10:03.704 --> 10:05.939
My dad's kinda
making me go.

10:05.972 --> 10:08.408
Your dad's making
you go to the dance?

10:08.441 --> 10:10.010
Man, what's that
all about?

10:10.811 --> 10:13.046
Who's your dad?
Hitler?

10:13.980 --> 10:14.915
(CHUCKLES)

10:14.948 --> 10:17.483
