you guys were gonna go...

10:17.518 --> 10:20.353
To make fun of people.
(CHUCKLES)

10:20.386 --> 10:21.555
That could be
kinda funny, right?

10:21.588 --> 10:22.689
KEN: I would go,

10:22.723 --> 10:26.159
but I have
a prior engagement.

10:26.192 --> 10:28.562
My cousin just sent me
a bunch of mushrooms,

10:28.595 --> 10:29.863
And I'm gonna eat them.

10:29.896 --> 10:32.065
Look, you know they're
gonna play disco.

10:32.098 --> 10:35.035
Right? Disco sucks.
I hate disco.

10:35.068 --> 10:36.402
<i>♪♪ Ooh ooh</i>

10:36.436 --> 10:38.772
<i>♪♪ Coo‐coo</i>
<i>coo coo‐coo ♪♪</i>

10:38.805 --> 10:41.074
