a girl who seems like
she needs a friend.

25:04.137 --> 25:06.172
So, come on, Linds.

25:07.207 --> 25:09.009
Talk to your buddy Jeff.

25:10.744 --> 25:11.878
Jeff...

25:12.713 --> 25:15.549
