the Cressman Conundrum.

25:45.512 --> 25:47.881
What the hell is that?

25:47.914 --> 25:51.017
Tom Cressman,
my freshman tormentor.

25:51.051 --> 25:53.587
The idea was,
if you fight your bully,

25:53.620 --> 25:55.756
afterwards,
whether you win
or lose,

25:55.789 --> 25:57.658
they'll tend
to leave you alone.

25:58.158 --> 25:59.359
Did it work?

25:59.392 --> 26:01.662
He broke my tailbone,
but the results
were effective.

26:01.695 --> 26:03.597
He got expelled.
It's a good plan.

26:03.630 --> 26:05.566
It's a terrible plan, okay?

26:05.599 --> 26:08.368
